{"id":"6100","name":"bright-early-field-of-broken-dreams-edition","title":"Bright &amp; Early: Field Of Broken Dreams Edition","author":"Christy Frink","date":"2010-11-22T09:45:00-06:00","tags":["american music awards","andrew jackson","brad paisley","cma music festival","cmapocalypse","cmapocalypse bingo","fort campbell","hermitage","lady antebellum","second harvest food bank","taylor swift","titans","veterans day","vince young"],"categories":["News"],"contentEncoded":"<div id=\"greet_block\"><noscript><div class=\"greet_block wpgb_cornered\"><div class=\"greet_text\"><div class=\"greet_image\"><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/feed/rss/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-greet-box/images/rss_icon.png\" alt=\"WP Greet Box icon\"></a></div>Hello there! If you&apos;re new to Nashvillest, you might want to <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/nashvillest\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>subscribe to our RSS feed</strong></a> to make sure you don&apos;t miss anything! We&apos;re also on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/nashvillest\" target=\"blank\"><strong>Twitter</strong></a> if you&apos;d like to join us there!<div style=\"clear:both\"></div><div class=\"greet_block_powered_by\">Powered by <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/projects/wordpress-plugins/wp-greet-box-wordpress-plugin/\" title=\"WP Greet Box WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WP Greet Box</a> <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/\" title=\"WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WordPress Plugin</a></div><div style=\"clear:both\"></div></div></div></noscript></div><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/fallingwater123/5194925758/in/pool-715021@N24/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://farm5.static.flickr.com/4110/5194925758_6be33a4c5e.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\"></a></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\">Good morning, Nashville. This week is off to a hurried &#xA0;start, so here&#x2019;s your quick sprint through the morning news:</p><ul><li>We were all scratching our heads when U2 announced a date at Vanderbilt, but it turns out that <a href=\"http://www.fox17.com/template/inews_wire/wires.regional.tn/22d73cf2-www.fox17.com.shtml\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.fox17.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">they actually approached LP Field first and were turned down. The CMApocalypse contract states that no concerts are to be held at the stadium within 30-45 days of CMA Fest</a>. Rest assured we&#x2019;ll find some way to include this in next year&#x2019;s CMApocalypse Bingo board.</li><li><a href=\"http://www.newschannel5.com/Global/story.asp?S=13546575\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.newschannel5.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">The Titans lost yesterday and VY&#x2122;&#xA0;threw a fit</a>. And he injured his hand! It was a banner day all around.</li><li>Titans fans, however, racked up a huge win for the community by <a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/Global/story.asp?S=13546413\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">donating 20,000 pounds of food to the Second Harvest Food Bank</a>.</li><li>Oh, and there was this one incredibly heartwarming moment where <a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/article/20101122/NEWS01/11220320/-1/RSS05\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">a Fort Campbell soldier completely surprised his family by coming home early from Afghanistan and meeting them in the middle of LP Field</a>.</li><li>Nashville had some great representation at the AMAs with <a href=\"http://blogs.tennessean.com/tunein/2010/11/22/bieber-becomes-youngest-winner/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;blogs.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Taylor Swift, Lady Antebellum and Brad Paisley bringing home awards</a>.</li><li>The Hermitage is almost finished with its <a href=\"http://www.fox17.com/template/inews_wire/wires.regional.tn/20d7458d-www.fox17.com.shtml\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.fox17.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">14-month, $1.2 million restoration project</a>.</li><li>Enjoy the nice weather while it lasts! <a href=\"http://nashvillewx.com/2010/11/warm-windy-day/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;nashvillewx.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Rain and cooler temperatures are on the way</a>.</li></ul><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><em>Photo by <a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/fallingwater123/5194925758/in/pool-715021@N24/\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">fallingwater123</a>.</em></p><p>Related posts:<ol><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2009/12/18/bright-early-crushing-our-dreams-edition/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Bright &amp; Early: Crushing Our Dreams Edition\">Bright &amp; Early: Crushing Our Dreams Edition</a></li><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2008/08/13/adventures-in-kentucky-franklin-drive-in-field-trips/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Adventures In Kentucky: Franklin Drive-In [Field Trips]\">Adventures In Kentucky: Franklin Drive-In [Field Trips]</a></li></ol></p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--END .entry-content .article-->"}